IMAPAccount balena
Host imap.gmail.com
User juan@balena.io
PassCmd +"pass key work/resin/gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions SSLv3
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem

IMAPStore balena-remote
Account balena

MaildirStore balena-local
Path ~/Mail/Balena
Inbox ~/Mail/Balena/INBOX

Channel balena-inbox
Master :balena-remote:
Slave :balena-local:
Patterns "INBOX"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel balena-trash
Master :balena-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :balena-local:"Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Channel balena-spam
Master :balena-remote:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :balena-local:"Spam"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group balena
Channel balena-inbox
Channel balena-trash
Channel balena-spam
